componentSets.name: Panel - form (Beta)
componentSets.description:
🚧This component is in Beta, enhancement to the current component in UI library soon 🚧 Panel to use in forms during creation or edit flows.
The panel is composed of the Heading and the Slot area.Heading that can contain props for metadata and actions that you can use as needed in the specific flow.
Slot, this is reserved for the content area, and you can replace it based functionality.
